column2: This recipe uses chopped apple and apple juice to make delicious apple muffins from scratch
This recipe for coconut bar cookies came to me from my maternal Gramie Watson and quickly became a most-requested item at the kids' schools as well as at church and other venues where it was sampled.
These are great on a summers day or on a whim, especially with lightly sweetened ice tea. They hold the taste of coconut and banana with flecks of pineapple and kiwi.
